title: Grouped Treemap
short-description: A zoomable treemap of grouped items. The example search looks at the _internal index.

title: Timeline Treemap
short-description: A flat treemap with a timeline and play button. The example search looks at the _internal index.

title: Simple Scatterplot
short-description: A simple scatterplot chart. The example compares cylinders, mpg, and horsepower of various cars from the 'auto-mpg' dataset.

title: Timeline Scatterplot
short-description: A scatterplot chart that includes a timeline. The examples looks the _internal index.

title: Boxplot
short-description: A boxplot/scatterplot combo, including top and bottom tukey, and interquartile ranges. The data comes from the 1994 US census.

title: Documentation
short-description: An excerpt of documentation from d3plus with some notes.
